IncluDo App
This application is an operational structure for IncluDo, a hypothetical training company for immigrants and disadvantaged people.

Requirements
Node.js (recommended version: 14.x or higher)
npm (recommended version: 6.x or higher)

Installation and Usage
Download the .zip folder or clone the repository:

git clone https://github.com/Fran-Lis/progetto_TypeScript
cd progetto_TypeScript

Install the dependencies:
In the Terminal or PowerShell, run the command:
npm install

Compile TypeScript into JavaScript:
Run the command:
tsc app.ts

Run the application:
Run the command:
node app.js

The names of people and companies used in the examples are fictitious, any reference to any real people and companies is purely coincidental.